sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as DSP API Server
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant WC as workflow-controller<br/>9090/TCP metrics<br/>6060/TCP health
    participant Pod as Workflow Step Pod
    participant Init as argoexec (init)<br/>Init Container
    participant Wait as argoexec (wait)<br/>Emissary Sidecar
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL/MariaDB<br/>5432/3306 TCP

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Workflow Execution (Pipeline Run)

    DSP->>K8s: POST Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    activate K8s
    K8s-->>DSP: Workflow created
    deactivate K8s

    WC->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>WC: New Workflow event

    loop For each workflow step
        WC->>K8s: Create Pod (with argoexec sidecar)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8s-->>WC: Pod created

        activate Pod
        Note over Pod,Init: Pod starts - init container runs first

        Init->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>Auth: Secret-based credentials
        S3-->>Init: Artifact data
        Note over Init: Stage scripts to<br/>/var/run/argo/

        Note over Pod,Wait: Main container executes step

        Wait->>K8s: Patch pod annotations (progress)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8s-->>Wait: Updated

        Wait->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>Auth: Secret-based credentials
        S3-->>Wait: Upload confirmed

        Wait->>K8s: Create/Patch WorkflowTaskResult CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8s-->>Wait: Result recorded
        deactivate Pod
    end

    WC->>K8s: Update Workflow status (completed)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>WC: Status updated

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 2: Workflow Archiving (Optional)

    WC->>K8s: Watch completed Workflows<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>WC: Completed Workflow event

    WC->>DB: Archive workflow data<br/>Auth: Secret-based username/password<br/>Encryption: Optional SSL/TLS
    DB-->>WC: Archived

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 3: CronWorkflow Scheduling

    WC->>K8s: Watch CronWorkflow CRs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>WC: CronWorkflow schedule triggered

    WC->>K8s: Create Workflow CR from template<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>WC: Workflow created
